    "title": "Simulating an external display or CarPlay"
  },
  "primaryContentSections": [
    {
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "Overview",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Overview",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Some iPhone and iPad devices support a wired connection to an external display. When you plug your compatible device into a supported external display, the device mirrors its display to the external display.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "In addition to external displays, iPhone devices running iOS 12.0 and later support connecting to CarPlay compatible vehicles. For more information on supporting CarPlay in your app, see ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/CarPlay",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ".",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Test your app’s support of external displays or CarPlay in Simulator during development, then test on actual devices.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "anchor": "Enable-an-external-display-or-CarPlay",
          "level": 3,
          "text": "Enable an external display or CarPlay",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "First, build and run your app in Simulator. For more information, see ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.Xcode/documentation/Xcode/running-your-app-in-simulator-or-on-a-device",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ".",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "When your app is running in Simulator, choose I/O > External Displays, then select an external display size or CarPlay. The supported options are:",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "items": [
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "640x480",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "720x480",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "1024x768",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "1280x720 (720p)",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "1920x1080 (1080p)",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "3840x2160 (4K)",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "CarPlay",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "type": "unorderedList"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Simulator opens a new window for the external display with the selected size.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Close the external display window, or choose I/O > External Displays > Disable to simulate unplugging from the external display.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    }
  ],
